headline: GTA Online
subtitle: This Week’s Podium, LS Car Meet Prize Ride and Test Track Vehicles
content:
Head over to The Diamond Casino & Resort to give the Lucky Wheel a spin. This week’s big winners receive a new Lampadati Casco.

LS Car Meet members who manage to place in the Top 4 in an LS Car Meet Series Race for 6 days in a row will earn themselves an Übermacht Cypher to spiff up as they see fit.

Plus, try out the Annis ZR350, Karin Futo GTX, and Karin Previon on the Car Meet’s Test Track.
